				     style

this project's style mirrors the linux kernel style[1], with the following
distinctions:

- use tabs to match the indentation level, but spaces for alignment:

	if(some_condition) {
		function_call(some_argument,
	(tab)	              some_other_argument);
		--------------
		^ spaces
	}

- to be added if anything comes up

[1] https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/torvalds/linux.git/tree/Documentation/process/coding-style.rst
